Class EditPhotoView

  • java.lang.Object
    • pda.view.EditPhotoView

  • public class EditPhotoView
extends java.lang.Object
    The EditPhotoView is the most important page of the application
    It display a chosen photo and allow to do effects on it.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Florent Catiau-Tristant and Mehdi Haddad

      • creerInterface

        private void creerInterface()
        Create the interface of the EditPhotoView page.
        It contains :
        • The name of the page : EditPhoto
        • 4 directory buttons (which contains some effects)
        • All the effect buttons
        • 5 Edition button (save, undo/redo, cancel, exit)
        • The chosen image
